  "title": "登顶开源 SOTA！上交大&小红书 LoopTool 实现工具调用任务的「数据进化」",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MzI4MjgzMw==&mid=2651002598&idx=2&sn=e446ea5f10fd98a66c99395f20cd57bf",
  "date": "2025-11-19 04:04:00",
  "author": "机器之心",
